item.title: Ep. 560 w/ Nicole Sodoma Attorney and Managing Principal Sodoma Law
item.description: I am the Founder and Managing Principal of Sodoma Law. In addition to my 20+ year practice of family law, I am a parenting coordinator, collaborative attorney, speaker and published author. In 2023, we opened our fifth Sodoma Law location with the goal of continuing to help families across the North Carolina and South Carolina regions. item.title: It's 2024, Happy New Year
item.description: Host Reed Galen shares the Lincoln Project’s plan for 2024 and how this is the year that everything has been building to. Plus, why our nation’s present moment is a simple binary, how the upcoming third anniversary of January 6th continues to inform this moment, and why Donald Trump facing justice for his crimes is the only path forward for American democracy.
